Zapatero to Announce on April 2 He Won’t Run in 2012, Mundo Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-03-21T07:27:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/zapatero-to-announce-on-april-2-he-won-t-run-in-2012-mundo-says.html
Spanish Prime Minister Jose Luis
Rodriguez Zapatero may announce on April 2 that he won’t stand
as a candidate in the 2012 general elections,  El Mundo  reported,
without citing anyone.  If Zapatero makes the announcement on April 2, the
Socialist party may name his successor as early as April 19, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net  